description: Idun Industrier AB engages in investing and developing industrial and service activities. The company is headquartered in Stockholm, Stockholm and currently employs 462 full-time employees. The company went IPO on 2021-03-25. The firm is a development and ownership partner for small and medium-sized companies operating in two areas - Manufacturing and Service & Maintenance. Idun Industrier consists of over 10 group companies, all of which are based in Sweden, but often with an international presence.
naicsSubsector: Securities, Commodity Contracts, and Other Financial Investments and Related Activities
